Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:04.39,Default,U,0,0,0,,3…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:05.34,2prop,U,0,0,0,,{\pos(619,651)}due
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:05.34,Default,U,0,0,0,,2…
